# 4️⃣ Features

## 🏠 4.1 Home Page

### Purpose:

Quick introduction + strong first impression.

### Sections:

* Hero Section

  * Name
  * Title (Full Stack Developer | MERN | Next.js)
  * Short tagline
  * CTA buttons:

    * View Projects
    * Contact Me

* Quick About Summary (2–3 lines)

* Tech Stack Preview

---

## 👨‍💻 4.2 About Page

### Sections:

* Detailed introduction
* Education
* Experience
* Skills breakdown:

  * Frontend
  * Backend
  * Database
  * DevOps
  * Tools

Optional:

* Download CV button

---

## 🚀 4.3 Projects Page (Most Important)

Each project should include:

* Project Title
* Description
* Tech Stack
* Features
* Screenshots
* Live Demo Link
* GitHub Link
* Technical Challenges
* What You Learned

Example Projects You Should Include:

* Admin Notification System
* Event Management System
* Consultancy Website (Next.js + Prisma)

